section.def:
class
                (類別), in relation to gas installation work, means
            a class of gas installation work specified in Part 2 of Schedule 1;

register
                (註冊紀錄冊) means the register kept under
                regulation 29;

paragraph.content:
the applicant is qualified under regulation 4 to be so
                    registered;
                    and

stating his name and the words “REGISTERED GAS CONTRACTOR NUMBER . . .
                ”
                or characters “註冊氣體工程承辦商號碼 . . .”;

subparagraph.content:
whose registration was obtained by fraud or
                        misrepresentation
                        in a material particular;

who it appears to the Authority has not complied with a requirement
                        under the Ordinance with which it is his obligation to comply;
                        or

paragraph.content:
where issued to a gas installer, be deemed to have been
                                        issued under regulation 8;
                                        or
